headline: Trump Campaign Plans Statewide Blitz on Caucus Day, to Put ‘Democrats on Notice’
abstract: Roughly 80 members of Congress, cabinet secretaries and administration officials will descend on the state to drive voter enthusiasm and make a show of force.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — The Iowa caucuses on Monday will be a competitive race for only one party, the Democrats, but President Trump’s campaign does not see it that way.
